# 导出

## 创建导出数据文件目录

```SQL
create directory DATA_EXPDP_DIR as '/tmp'; 
```

## 执行导出命令

```SQL
expdp \'/ as sysdba\' schemas=SDP_CMS_HRB DIRECTORY=DATA_EXPDP_DIR DUMPFILE=SDP_CMS_HRBBAK_20200607.DMP LOGFILE=SDP_CMS_HRBBAK_20200607.LOG
```

